title: Deathstroke (001 - 060 + Annuals) (1991 - 1996) (digital) (Minut
description:
Deathstroke (001 - 060 + Annuals) (1991 - 1996) (digital) (Minutemen-Midas)


Longtime Teen Titan foe and notorious mercenary for hire Slade Wilson began his impressive 60 issue run with the help of writer Marv Wolfman and artist Steve Irwin. The series 1st issue retold Deathstroke's traumatic past and re-established his relationship with his right hand man Wintergreen. It also served to introduce a new Ravager, a villain bearing the monicker of Deathstroke's deceased son, Grant. As the series progressed, Deathstroke would go on to fight the Dark Knight, join forces with a new female Vigilante, and even make a costume change inti a dramatic blue and black uniform
